Parse Real CTI Reports and Map to ATT&CK
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Extract threat intelligence indicators from CTI reports using Python
Map extracted indicators to MITRE ATT&CK tactics and techniques
Create ATT&CK Navigator layer files for visualization
Generate actionable intelligence reports for red team operations
Prerequisites
Basic Python programming knowledge
Understanding of cybersecurity fundamentals
Familiarity with Linux command line
Basic knowledge of MITRE ATT&CK framework
